WEBVTT

00:05.219 --> 00:10.222
Deep in the woods, there's a village filled with joyful and happy Smurfs.

00:10.539 --> 00:15.509
And one particularly handsome, suave, deep-voiced Smurf,...

00:15.637 --> 00:16.620
...whose every word...

00:16.697 --> 00:19.239
Okay, narrator Smurf, that'll do.

00:19.400 --> 00:20.573
Oh, all right.

00:21.045 --> 00:22.441
But not too far away,...

00:22.715 --> 00:27.499
...the evil wizard Gargamel is up to something diabolical.

00:28.270 --> 00:30.260
I am making my own creations...

00:30.652 --> 00:34.703
...to help me finally capture the Smurfs.

00:34.975 --> 00:37.653
I will call them the Naughties.

00:40.027 --> 00:41.143
Where are we?

00:41.311 --> 00:41.728
It worked!

00:44.297 --> 00:44.803
Close enough.

00:45.948 --> 00:47.841
From Sony Pictures Animation.

00:47.899 --> 00:48.981
Naughties, attack!

00:51.545 --> 00:52.493
Here's my plan.

00:52.587 --> 00:55.105
We trick Smurfette into being naughty like us.

00:55.619 --> 00:58.249
And she'll have so much fun, she'll never go back.

00:58.355 --> 00:59.905
Oh dear, catch please.

01:01.337 --> 01:04.071
Don't worry, Smurfette could never be naughty.

01:04.198 --> 01:06.234
Why are we going so slow?

01:07.463 --> 01:08.199
Let's go!

01:08.503 --> 01:09.547
Naughty, naughty.

01:10.447 --> 01:11.568
Isn't this fun?

01:12.281 --> 01:13.330
Decidedly not!

01:14.148 --> 01:15.836
The Smurfs 2.

01:15.949 --> 01:17.705
Smurfs!

01:18.231 --> 01:19.548
Guys, I'm just smurfing with you.

01:19.769 --> 01:21.555
That is an excellent impression.

